    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387670/extras/ff655090d5511fdb8b5667f0fd912260.avif?t=1765958772\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《As One We Survive》是一款俯视视角的末日生存游戏，背景设定在被灾难摧毁的美国。你将扮演一位父亲，在“电网瘫痪”的后疫情时代，为患病的女儿寻找帮助。战斗、搜寻、制作并收集资源，让家人得以生存下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过独特融合的生存与社区经营玩法，你必须建立一个幸存者社区，既要活下去，也要为女儿找到希望。建设并管理你的社区，保护成员免受危险，在残酷无情的世界中做出艰难抉择，决定团队的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387670/extras/01e19795590ba3a842c5fbc794f3c571.poster.avif?t=1765958772\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387670/extras/01e19795590ba3a842c5fbc794f3c571.webm?t=1765958772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387670/extras/01e19795590ba3a842c5fbc794f3c571.mp4?t=1765958772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>艰难求生：</strong> 在危机四伏、资源稀缺的荒野中搜刮、制作，并想尽办法生存。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>残酷战斗：</strong> 没有急救包；用绷带止血，通过睡眠治疗伤势，并保持武器的可靠性。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>社区管理：</strong> 加入幸存者社区，升级基地设施，创造可再生资源以支撑团队生计。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>同伴系统：</strong> 与其他幸存者结下羁绊，一同外出搜寻重要物资，了解你的社区成员。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>技能成长：</strong> 在荒野中磨炼生存技巧，每次挑战都让你更强。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>两种玩法：</strong> 故事模式与生存模式。先体验剧情，再在末世中独自或与同伴挑战极限。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387670/extras/f9fb08650b4eac0bdde38da7fabcca0f.poster.avif?t=1765958772\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387670/extras/f9fb08650b4eac0bdde38da7fabcca0f.webm?t=1765958772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387670/extras/f9fb08650b4eac0bdde38da7fabcca0f.mp4?t=1765958772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>游戏循环</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>建立社区：</strong> 招募幸存者，共同打造安全避风港。<br> <br><strong>补给行动：</strong> 收集食物、饮用水和药品以维持生存。<br> <br><strong>建造与资源：</strong> 建设设施，发展可再生生产。<br> <br>       <strong>推进任务：</strong> 从新成员处获取情报，推动剧情发展，帮助你的女儿。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387670/extras/09a4136a2ef9d7372966d821b5be26c5.poster.avif?t=1765958772\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387670/extras/09a4136a2ef9d7372966d821b5be26c5.webm?t=1765958772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387670/extras/09a4136a2ef9d7372966d821b5be26c5.mp4?t=1765958772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
